<!-- Node: "Warren Spector (Ion Storm) Talks Thief: Deadly Shadows" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Warren Spector (Ion Storm) Talks Thief: Deadly Shadows</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2" title="View user profile.">Gard</a> on Thursday, March 4, 2004 - 02:40</small><br /><br />
<p><a href="http://www.gamespy.com/interviews/march04/spector/">GameSpy.com</a> has a four page interview with Warren Spector, the Studio Director of Ion Storm, who talks about their new title <i>Thief: Deadly Shadows</i> and the controvesy(?) over <i>Deus Ex: Invisible War</i>.</p>

