<div class="body_box_header">Cypress Hill new single!!</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/1804" title="View user profile.">Kingpin_Xatrix</a> on Monday, March 1, 2004 - 19:09</small><br /><br />
<p align = "center"><img src = "http://www.cypresshill.com/images/WhatsYourNumberWeb.jpg"></p>

<p>If you're one of <b>Cypress Hill</b> fans you'll be happy to know that they released new single, called <a href = "http://www.cypressonline.com/">What's Your Number?</a>.</p>

<p>In the past, Cypress Hill made official soundtrack for <b>Kingpin:Life of Crime</b> by <b>Xatrix Entertainment, Inc.</b> Xatrix aka <a href = "http://www.gmistudios.com/">Gray Matter Studios, Inc.</a> working on a new game. From their previous games, like Redneck Rampage, Kingpin and RTCW, I'm sure it'll be some cool game.
